- Read `docs/standards/engineering/workflow.md` for commit and branch naming.

# Scripts

- Use `#!/usr/bin/env bash` and `set -euo pipefail`
- Must work on both macOS and Linux
- Document usage in a comment at the top
- Exit with non-zero on failure — CI depends on exit codes
- New scripts should be wired into package.json, git hooks, or CI
